description:
Acoustica MP3 CD Burner v4.71b151 made Portable (Thinstall).

No need to install it!
Or, if you want to, Setup and Keygen are included.


Easily Burn DJ style music CDs or MP3 CDs! Not only will it burn your music in the order you want it, but it will let you edit each song to get rid of silence, extra long applauses or fade in and out incomplete songs! Burn all the major types of audio files, including MP3, OGG, WMA and WAV. Rip your CDs to make your own MP3, OGG, WMA or WAVs! Easily create professional DJ cross fades or 'segues' between tracks. Boost or EQ tracks so that you don't have to constantly adjust the volume dial on your stereo! 


More infos at
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.acoustica.com/mp3-cd-burner/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
